  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA42">
<l>niṉaippaṉ ṟirumālai nīṇṭatōḷ kāṇa</l>
<l>niṉaippār piṟappoṉṟu nērār – maṉaippāṟ</l>
<l>piṟantār piṟanteytum pēriṉpa mellān</l>
<l>tuṟantār toḻutārat tōḷ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I think of Tirumāl in order to see his extended arms.</l>
<l>Those who think [thus] are not due for [another] birth. Those born</l>
<l>in the house, those who worship  those arms have abandoned</l>
<l>all the great pleasures obtained from being born.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
